    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone looking for a functional daily driver. While the car runs and drives well, the exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior shows signs of significant use, including some wear on the upholstery. It has been regularly serviced, though it may soon require attention to minor items like suspension bushings or a small oil leak. This is a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
